<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="specifying-xml-files-search-paths" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Specifying XML Files Search Path</title>
  <taskbody id="body">
    <context>
      <p>The environment variable    <codeph>
          <varname>$SERNA_XML</varname>
        </codeph>that contains the path to XML files is for advanced operations only. This variable is used in Serna configuration files and in  <filepath>*.bat</filepath> files necessary for publishing.</p>
      <p>To specify the value of <codeph>
          <varname>$SERNA_XML</varname>
        </codeph>, do the following:</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>To call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>, choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>Tools</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Preferences</uicontrol>
            </menucascade>.</p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Select the <keyword>Search Paths tab</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <fig>
            <title>Search Paths tab.</title>
            <image href="preferences-dialog-search-paths-tab.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          </fig>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Browse</uicontrol> button next to the <uicontrol>XML files path (value of $SERNA_XML)</uicontrol> field.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>In the <keyword>Browse For Folder Dialog</keyword>, select a directory and click <uicontrol>OK</uicontrol>.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Apply</uicontrol> button to apply the settings.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Close</uicontrol> button to close the dialog.</cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>
